《'''自由髮則'''》是美国女歌手[[Lady_Gaga|Lady Gaga]]在第二张录音室专辑《天生完美》中的一首歌，由Gaga和RedOne合写和制作。《自由髮則》在2011年5月16日作为iTunes Store"Countdown to Born This Way"减价活动的促销单曲以数位下载形式向全球发布。<ref>{{cite press release |url=http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/itunes-countdown-to-lady-gagas-born-this-way-album-kicks-off-today-with-new-single-the-edge-of-glory-121521049.html|title=iTunes Countdown to Lady Gaga's Born This Way Album Kicks Off Today With New Single "The Edge of Glory" |date=2011-05-12  |publisher=[[Interscope_Records|Interscope Records]] |accessdate=2011-05-15}}</ref>之前的促销单曲是《[[The_Edge_Of_Glory|The Edge Of Glory]]》（这首歌后来作为专辑单曲发布）。然而Gaga称《自由髮則》不打算作为专辑单曲发布，除非像《[[The_Edge_Of_Glory|The Edge Of Glory]]》那样在iTunes Store 上面畅销。

Gaga称《自由髮則》像是金属乐队[[Kiss|Kiss合唱团]]和[[铁娘子乐队|铁娘子乐队]]的作品，并受[[布魯斯·斯普林斯廷|布魯斯·斯普林斯廷]]影响。这首快节奏的club record受Gaga青少年时期父母干涉其穿着的经历的影响Gaga发现只有通过头发是唯一能够表达自己的方式，并将其描述为关于自由和自我改变之歌。歌词谈论了拥抱自己的发型，根本上是表达了自由的理念。《自由髮則》在The Monster Ball欧洲巡演期间录制。这首歌也含有来自[[克拉伦斯·克莱蒙斯|克拉伦斯·克莱蒙斯]]的萨克斯管演奏。

《自由髮則》因其表达的自我解放、自我主义和赋权而受到赞誉，尽管有些人认为“头发”这一意象表达自由不太新颖。《自由髮則》在主要音乐市场入榜，在新西兰和苏格兰进入榜单前十。在其他的国家（包括美国市场的[[Billboard_Hot_100|''Billboard'' Hot 100]]）上面排在前二十。Gaga在早安美国、英国的Paul O'Grady Live、The Howard Stern Show上表演此歌。之后这首歌被加入Born This Way Ball的表演单。

==背景和发布==

《自由髮則》由Gaga和RedOne合写，歌名于2011年2月在[[时尚_(杂志)|Vogue]]杂志的访谈中透露。<ref name="mtvre">{{cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1663980/lady-gaga-hair.jhtml|title=Lady Gaga's 'Hair' Embraces Style Freedom|last=Vena|first=Jocelyn|date=2011-05-17|accessdate=2011-05-17|publisher=[[MTV|MTV]] ([[MTV_Networks|MTV Networks]])}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.vogue.com/magazine/article/lady-gaga-our-lady-of-pop/ |title=Lady Gaga: Our Lady of Pop |first=Jonathan |last=Van Meter |date=2011-02-04 |work=[[Vogue_(magazine)|Vogue]] |publisher=[[Condé_Nast_Publications|Condé Nast Publications]] |accessdate=2011-05-15 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110512204613/http://www.vogue.com/magazine/article/lady-gaga-our-lady-of-pop/ |archivedate=2011-05-12 }}</ref>在[[The_Graham_Norton_Show|The Graham Norton Show]]上面，Gaga解释了这首歌的创作来源：Gaga把头发类比为自由，并且头发是她身上唯一不受他人决定、能够自己改变的部位。<ref>{{cite episode |people=Lady Gaga|title=[[The_Graham_Norton_Show|Lady Gaga – Graham Norton 5?13?11]] |airdate=2011-05-13|format=HD|medium=Transcription|city=London|network=[[BBC_Online|BBC Online]]|time=15:12|credits=[[Graham_Norton|Graham Norton]]}}</ref>根据某媒体在二月发布的消息，《自由髮則》另一灵感来自[[佩特·班纳塔|佩特·班纳塔]]的80年代音乐《We Belong》，并在主题上主要用了接近《Born This Way》的歌词。<ref name="mtvrelease">{{cite web |url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1663553/lady-gaga-hair-single.jhtml|title=Lady Gaga To Release New Born This Way Single 'Hair'|first=Jocelyn |last=Vena |date=2011-05-15 |publisher=[[MTV|MTV]] ([[MTV_Networks|MTV Networks]]) |accessdate=2011-05-17}}</ref>Gaga在Twitter账号上发了一条带视频的推文，进一步阐释了这首歌的灵感：“当我还是一个孩子的时候，每当我下楼时，父母会说，‘回到楼上，梳梳你的头发，换件衣服，你不能穿这个出门。’我感觉这就像是扼杀我的身份……我的头发是我的荣耀。它是我唯一可以改变自己的东西。”<ref name="art">{{cite web |url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/music/news/a319511/lady-gaga-reveals-hair-cover-art.html |title=Lady GaGa reveals 'Hair' cover art |first=Daniel |last=Sperling |date=2011-05-14 |publisher=[[Digital_Spy|Digital Spy]] |accessdate=2011-05-15}}</ref>

最初《自由髮則》被打算在2011年5月16日作为专辑的第二支促销单曲发布（前一首为《[[The_Edge_Of_Glory|The Edge Of Glory]]》）<ref name="rel">{{cite news|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/471660/lady-gagas-edge-of-glory-single-premieres-hair-coming-next-week|title=Lady Gaga's 'Edge of Glory' Single Premieres, 'Hair' Coming Next Week |first=Jason|last= Lipshutz |date=2011-05-09 |work=[[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]] |publisher=[[Prometheus_Global_Media|Prometheus Global Media]] |accessdate=2011-05-15}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://music-mix.ew.com/2011/05/10/lady-gaga-hair/|title=Lady Gaga to release fourth single, 'Hair,' a week before Born This Way's release: Still anxious for the full album?|last=Wete|first=Brad|date=2011-05-10|accessdate=2011-05-17|work=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]]|publisher=[[Time_Inc.|Time Inc.]]}}</ref>，然而后来《The Edge Of Glory》因为大受欢迎、销量可观而作为专辑单曲发布，于是《自由髮則》就成为了第一支促销单曲。<ref name="rel"/> Gaga称《自由髮則》不打算作为专辑单曲发布，除非像《[[The_Edge_Of_Glory|The Edge Of Glory]]》那样在iTunes Store 上面畅销。<ref name="art"/> Gaga在2011年5月13日在Twitter上发布《自由髮則》的CD封面。封面为黑白两色，描绘了粉红头发的Gaga躺在地板上，穿着一件锋利的皮革装，上面有突出的乳头钉。封面由Nick Knight拍摄。<ref name="mtvre"/><ref name="art"/><ref>{{cite web |url=http://neonlimelight.com/2011/05/14/lady-gaga-highlights-hair-release-with-single-cover/ |title=Lady Gaga Highlights "Hair" Release With Single Cover |author=TJ |date=2011-05-14 |publisher=Neon Limelight |accessdate=2011-05-15}}</ref>当天晚些时候Gaga发推：“Born This Way Itunes Countdown活动将发布我的歌曲《自由髮則》于2moro 1pm PST。”<ref>{{cite web |url=http://entertainment.xin.msn.com/en/celebrity/blogs/hollywood/Lady-Gaga.aspx?cp-documentid=4847821 |title=MSN: Lady Gaga Twitter |date=2011-05-15 |publisher=[[MSN|MSN]] |accessdate=2011-05-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120429133254/http://entertainment.xin.msn.com/en/celebrity/blogs/hollywood/Lady-Gaga.aspx?cp-documentid=4847821 |archive-date=2012-04-29 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>Gaga在Twitter发了一句歌词："I'll dye living just as free as my <nowiki>Hair</nowiki>!"随后补充说“dye”应为“die”。<ref name="mtvre"/>

==录制和作曲==

在On Air with Ryan Seacrest访谈中，Gagaa说《自由髮則》是一首快节奏的俱乐部歌曲（up-tempo club record），并受[[布鲁斯·斯普林斯廷|布鲁斯·斯普林斯廷]]影响。同时她透露了[[克拉伦斯·克莱蒙斯|克拉伦斯·克莱蒙斯]]参与了这首歌的萨克斯管演奏。<ref name="ryan">{{cite news |url=http://ryanseacrest.com/2011/02/15/lady-gaga-whitney-houston-was-my-vocal-idol-growing-up-audio/|title=Lady Gaga: Whitney Houston Was My Vocal Idol Growing Up |first=Sadao |last=Turner |date=2011-02-15 |work=[[On_Air_with_Ryan_Seacrest_(radio)|On Air with Ryan Seacrest]]|publisher= [[KIIS-FM|KIIS-FM]] |accessdate=2011-05-15}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1658332/lady-gaga-born-this-way.jhtml|title=Lady Gaga's Born This Way: What We Know So Far |first=Jocelyn |last=Vena |date=2011-05-08 |work= |publisher=[[MTV|MTV]] ([[MTV_Networks|MTV Networks]]) |accessdate=2011-05-15}}</ref>包括金属乐队[[Kiss合唱团|Kiss合唱团]]和[[铁娘子乐队|铁娘子乐队]]的作品也是对《自由髮則》曲调的另一影响。<ref name="ryan"/> 她在Seacrest's show上说《自由髮則》的作曲很有趣，因为它是带舞曲节拍的并置萨克斯（juxtaposing saxophone with a dance record）。<ref name="ryan"/> 在WHTZ|Z-100的采访中她补充：“其中有些主题在这张专辑上由更大的拓广。To put my money where my mouth is.”<ref name="mtvrelease"/> 萨克斯独奏有对[[E_Street_Band|E Street Band]]和[[Bruce_Springsteen|Bruce Springsteen]]音乐的参考；他们向她表现了另一种音乐体裁，同时又包含音乐所有不同元素。<ref name="record">{{cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1663887/lady-gaga-edge-of-glory.jhtml|title=Lady Gaga's 'Edge Of Glory' Is A 'Bold Move,' Co-Producer Says |first=Jocelyn|last=Vena|publisher=[[MTV|MTV]] ([[MTV_Networks|MTV Networks]])|date=2011-05-13|accessdate=2011-05-14}}</ref>最终她决定让[[克拉伦斯·克莱蒙斯|克拉伦斯·克莱蒙斯]]演奏萨克斯。<ref name="exclusive">{{cite news|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/exclusive-how-e-street-band-saxophonist-clarence-clemons-ended-up-on-lady-gagas-new-album-20110218|title=Exclusive: How E Street Band Saxophonist Clarence Clemons Ended Up on Lady Gaga's New Album|last=Greene|first=Andy|date=2011-02-18|accessdate=2011-05-13|work=[[Rolling_Stone|Rolling Stone]]|publisher=[[Jann_Wenner|Jann Wenner]]}}</ref>

==评论==
[[File:Clarence-Clemons.jpg|thumb]]的萨克斯演奏这首歌的亮点之一。]]
《自由髮則》获得的评论大多为好评。在The Monster Ball Tour最后一站的开始前一小时，Gaga向[[Rolling_Stone|Rolling Stone]]发了来自专辑《天生完美》的四首曲目，包括《无需多言》、《你和我》、《幸福边界》，来看看他们给的乐评。Matthew Perpetua写了一篇《自由髮則》的正面乐评，将其描述为“天生完美”的模中的另一首鼓舞人心的歌曲，但感觉比较怪诞，总结说这首歌将会变成“各地沙龙的圣歌”。<ref name="preview">{{cite news |url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/preview-six-songs-from-lady-gagas-born-this-way-20110218|title=An Early Report on Six Songs From Lady Gaga's 'Born This Way' |first=Matthew |last=Perpetua |date=2011-02-18|work=[[Rolling_Stone|Rolling Stone]] |publisher=[[Jann_Wenner|Jann Wenner]] |accessdate=2011-05-15}}</ref>同一媒体的Jody Rosen认为：“虽然Gaga不是第一个把自尊自由和自由发型联系在一起的歌手，但是是最以之为己任的。”<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/lady-gagas-born-this-way-a-track-by-track-breakdown-20110518|title=Lady Gaga's 'Born This Way': A Track-by-Track Breakdown|last=Rosen|first=Jody|date=2011-05-18|accessdate=2011-05-19|work=[[Rolling_Stone|Rolling Stone]]|publisher=[[Jann_Wenner|Jann Wenner]]}}</ref>[[NME|NME]]的Dan Martin将其分类为一个赋权圣歌，用了“风吹头发”的意象比同名单曲更为简单地表明了这张专辑的“爱你自己并Let-It-All-Hang-Out”的信息。这首歌曲通过成为长期以来最gay的东西，再次打出王牌。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.nme.com/reviews/lady-gaga/12061 |title=Album Review: Lady Gaga, 'Born This Way' |last=Martin |first=Dan |date=2011-05-17 |accessdate=2011-05-17 |work=[[NME|NME]] |publisher=[[IPC_Media|IPC Media]] |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5ylnIfKLf?url=http://www.nme.com/reviews/lady-gaga/12061 |archivedate=2011-05-18 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>[[卫报|卫报]]的Tim Jonze觉得这首歌传达的信息不是特别的新，毕竟60年代同名音乐剧也传达的同样信息。尽管他把部分歌词形容为“老调重弹”，他认为“这些缺点也可以成为优势，值得敬佩的是这首歌引导了迷惑中的青少年寻找自己的身份特性。”<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.theguardian.com/music/2011/may/18/lady-gaga-born-this-way-review|last=Jonze|first=Tim|date=2011-05-18|accessdate=2011-05-18|title=Lady Gaga: Born This Way – review|work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]|publisher=[[Guardian_News_and_Media|Guardian News and Media]]}}</ref>Leah Collins在[[The_Vancouver_Sun|The Vancouver Sun]]的报道中将其描述为"a pumping anthem designed to pump up your follicles with pride." 她补充说这首歌的总体感觉是复古舞曲（retro dance music）。<ref name="van">{{cite news |last=Collins |first=Leah |date=2011-05-17 |accessdate=2011-05-17 |work=[[The_Vancouver_Sun|The Vancouver Sun]] |publisher=Postmedia Network Inc. |title=Lady Gaga puts latest singles online |url=http://www.vancouversun.com/Lady+Gaga+puts+latest+singles+online+audio/4797565/story.html |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5ym3kAkPw?url=http://www.vancouversun.com/Lady+Gaga+puts+latest+singles+online+audio/4797565/story.html |archivedate=2011-05-18 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>
E! Online的Natalie Finn from对这首曲目感到失望，感觉专辑《天生完美》中发布的曲目虽然没有那么抓耳，他们都是关于一个同样主题“成为真正自我的重要性。噢，好，可能我们只是在等待下一个《[[Bad_Romance|Bad Romance]]》来让我们感觉飘飘欲仙，或是下一首《Speechless》让我们来哭泣，或者甚至下一首《Just Dance》让我们感觉舞力全开。”<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.eonline.com/news/242197/listen-now-lady-gaga-lets-her-hair-down|title=Listen Now: Lady Gaga Lets Her "Hair" Down|last=Finn|first=Natalie|date=2011-05-16|accessdate=2011-05-18|publisher=[[E!_Online|E! Online]]}}</ref>[[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]]的Jason Lipshultz感觉这首歌是另一首个人主义圣歌，把Gaga的头发作为她狂野性格的隐喻。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/471548/lady-gagas-hair-hits-itunes-listen|title=Lady Gaga's 'Hair' Hits iTunes: Listen|last=Lipshultz|first=Jason|date=2011-05-17|accessdate=2011-05-18|work=[[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]]|publisher=Prometheus Global Media}}</ref>

